These integrate directly into:
QA reports
Editorial logs
Trust metrics

4. How this wires into the pipeline
Pre-generation (Interpreter):
if (requiresForbiddenDomain(facts, refusalRules)) {
  return suppressConfiguration();
}

Post-generation (QA):
const violations = detectRefusalViolations(text, refusalRules);
if (violations.length) throw new RefusalError(violations);

No retries.
No “tone fixes.”
This is a hard stop.

5. What this file prevents (explicitly)
Astrology as medical advice
Astrology as prophecy
Astrology as moral authority
Astrology as fear machine
This is how you stay modern at scale.

